# Face ID / Touch ID / fingerprint — matching capture path.
#
# Exercises FlutterProbe v0.9.8's `enroll biometric` and `biometric match`
# steps. The app's BiometricLoginPage presents a Face ID prompt; a matching
# capture should unlock and navigate to the dashboard.
#
# Runtime requirements:
#   - iOS Simulator: nothing extra (probe.biometric_signal delivers the result)
#   - Android emulator: pre-enroll fingerprint ID 1 in Settings before run
#   - Physical devices: steps skip with a warning

before all tests
  enroll biometric

test "matching face unlocks the app"
  @smoke @biometric @happy
  open the app
  tap "Biometric Login"
  wait until "Sign in with Face ID" appears
  tap "Sign in with Face ID"
  biometric match
  wait until "Dashboard" appears
  see "Dashboard"

test "matching face works from a cold start"
  @biometric
  restart the app
  tap "Biometric Login"
  wait until "Sign in with Face ID" appears
  tap "Sign in with Face ID"
  biometric match
  see "Dashboard"
